{"tid":1847850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港郵政今日宣布，農曆新年假期後(即一月二十九日起)的郵件派遞，櫃位服務及郵箱收信服務將會暫停","createTime":"2020-01-28T08:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:37:53.000Z","uid":291338,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8517b5365c77ef69bfd63197aad1156063bd0b","tid":1847850,"uid":291338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"郵政服務特別安排<br />\n<br />\n就政府今日（一月二十八日）宣布實施的政府部門特別上班安排，香港郵政今日宣布，農曆新年假期後(即一月二十九日起)的郵件派遞，櫃位服務及郵箱收信服務將會暫停，但會維持入口特快專遞郵件派遞服務。<br />\n<br />\n有關安排暫定實行至二月二日，香港郵政屆時會再檢視情況。在此期間投寄的郵件會於郵政服務恢復正常<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/web_notices/webNoticesDetail.html?id=60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fweb_notices%2FwebNoticesDetail.html%3Fid%3D60&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=c47a7988\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/web_notices/webNoticesDetail.html?id=60</a>"},{"pid":"7c8d1e7df052adf4301b8002c249839a5da5cffe","tid":1847850,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtuFsHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtuFsHg.jpg&h=1d504957&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fF9k2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fF9k2g.jpg&h=ab4a427a&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>熱烈欢迎全国同胞來港免费就医！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847735</a></strong></span>"}]}